Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.24,0:22:27.80,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没地方下了啊 怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.35,0:22:31.81,gogo2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,372)}{\fnsimhei}{\c&HEFEFEF&}{\3c&HED0D10&}{\bord3}{\fs22}{\fad(200,250)}优希也… 没地方可下了
